</div></div></div><div class="wrap mcb-wrap one-second  valign-top clearfix" style="padding:0 0 0 2%" ><div class="mcb-wrap-inner"><div class="column mcb-column one column_column  column-margin-"><div class="column_attr clearfix"  style=""><h5>COVERING THE ENTIRE BAY AREA</h5>
<p class="big">I, unlike most real estate agents, cover the entire Bay area, which means I work with clients as far south as San Jose, as far East as Livermore, as far North as Walnut Creek. In addition, I cover the entire East Bay, Peninsula and San Francisco.</p>

<h5>TAKING CARE OF YOU</h5>
<p class="big"> Now I can take care of you! I am familiar with all the neighborhoods in all these different cities and can help you narrow down which specific neighborhoods would be the best match for you and yours. I love working with buyers and have become a powerhouse at matching clients to their ideal property, often times on the very first home tour!</p></div></div></div></div><div class="wrap mcb-wrap one-second  valign-top clearfix" style="padding:0 2% 0 0" ><div class="mcb-wrap-inner"><div class="column mcb-column one column_column  column-margin-"><div class="column_attr clearfix"  style=""><p><span class="dropcap size-2" >I</span>
 am your trailblazer for buying or selling anywhere in the SF Bay Area.  My clients call me The Tigress.</p>

<p>Wonder why?</p>
 
<p>It's because I go above and beyond clients expectations consistently delivering better-than-expected results. When I am selling, I get double the exposure for a home compared to other agents to maximize competition. Negotiation is my super power. When other agents advise you to take the best offer, I aggressively negotiate every one for the best possible price and fast closing.</p>
 
<p>If you are my buyer, I will go above and beyond to ensure you dont just get an acceptable house, but will do my best to get you into the house of your dreams.</p>
 
<p>I truly have my clients interest at heart. If the timing isnt best to sell, Ill advise to wait however long it takes to get top dollar for your home. I am very knowledgeable about San Francisco real estate as well as many other neighborhoods across the Bay Area.</p>


